<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>{{ subject }}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f0f4f8;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#1a202c;">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#f0f4f8;">
  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="padding:24px 16px;">

      <!-- Container principal -->
      <table width="640" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
             style="max-width:640px;width:100%;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:8px;
                    box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);overflow:hidden;">

        <!-- Cabeçalho -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background-color:#1a4a7a;padding:28px 32px 24px;">
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-size:11px;color:#93c5fd;text-transform:uppercase;
                             letter-spacing:1px;">Monitoramento de Qualidade da Água</p>
                  <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:22px;color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;line-height:1.3;">
                    Boletim Semanal — Lagoas Costeiras
                  </h1>
                  <p style="margin:8px 0 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#bfdbfe;">
                    Litoral Norte do RS &nbsp;·&nbsp; Período: <strong>{{ report_period }}</strong>
                  </p>
                </td>
                <td align="right" valign="top" style="white-space:nowrap;">
                  <p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#93c5fd;">Gerado em</p>
                  <p style="margin:4px 0 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#ffffff;font-weight:600;">
                    {{ generated_at }}
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Bloco de alertas críticos / elevados -->
        {% set alert_lagoas = lagoas | selectattr("status", "in", ["critico", "elevado"]) | list %}
        {% if alert_lagoas %}
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:0 32px;">
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
                   style="margin-top:20px;background-color:#fff7ed;border-left:4px solid #ea580c;
                          border-radius:4px;padding:16px;">
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:16px;">
                  <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#9a3412;">
                    ⚠ ATENÇÃO — Lagoas com nível elevado ou crítico de clorofila
                  </p>
                  {% for lg in alert_lagoas %}
                  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
                         style="margin-bottom:6px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="font-size:13px;color:#7c2d12;">
                        <strong>{{ lg.lagoa }}</strong>
                        &nbsp;·&nbsp;
                        NDCI médio: <strong>{{ "%.4f"|format(lg.ndci_mean) if lg.ndci_mean is not none else "—" }}</strong>
                        &nbsp;·&nbsp;
                        <span style="background-color:{{ lg.status_color }};color:#fff;
                                     padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;">
                          {{ lg.status | upper }}
                        </span>
                        &nbsp;·&nbsp; Observação: <strong>{{ lg.data }}</strong>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  {% endfor %}
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endif %}

        <!-- Seção: tabela de status por lagoa -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:24px 32px 8px;">
            <h2 style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#1a4a7a;
                       border-bottom:2px solid #e2e8f0;padding-bottom:8px;">
              Status por Lagoa — Observações Recentes
            </h2>
            <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:12px;color:#64748b;">
              Janela de busca: últimos <strong>{{ lookback_days }} dias</strong>.
              Metodologia: NDCI/Sentinel-2 por imagem individual
              (Pi &amp; Guasselli, SBSR 2025).
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:0 32px 24px;">
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
                   style="border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;">
              <!-- Cabeçalho da tabela -->
              <tr style="background-color:#1a4a7a;color:#ffffff;">
                <th style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;
                           border-radius:4px 0 0 0;">Lagoa</th>
                <th style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;font-weight:600;">
                  Observação</th>
                <th style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;font-weight:600;">
                  NDCI médio</th>
                <th style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;font-weight:600;">
                  NDCI P90</th>
                <th style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;font-weight:600;">
                  Turbidez</th>
                <th style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;font-weight:600;">
                  Pixels</th>
                <th style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;font-weight:600;
                           border-radius:0 4px 0 0;">Status</th>
              </tr>

              {% for lg in lagoas %}
              <tr style="background-color:{{ '#f8fafc' if loop.index is odd else '#ffffff' }};
                         border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">
                <td style="padding:10px 12px;font-weight:600;color:#1e293b;">
                  {{ lg.lagoa }}
                </td>
                <td style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;color:#475569;">
                  {% if lg.sem_observacao_recente %}
                    <span style="color:#94a3b8;font-style:italic;">Sem dados recentes</span>
                  {% else %}
                    {{ lg.data }}
                  {% endif %}
                </td>
                <td style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;color:#1e293b;">
                  {{ "%.4f"|format(lg.ndci_mean) if lg.ndci_mean is not none else "—" }}
                </td>
                <td style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;color:#1e293b;">
                  {{ "%.4f"|format(lg.ndci_p90) if lg.ndci_p90 is not none else "—" }}
                </td>
                <td style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;color:#1e293b;">
                  {{ "%.4f"|format(lg.ndti_mean) if lg.ndti_mean is not none else "—" }}
                </td>
                <td style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;color:#475569;">
                  {% if lg.n_pixels is not none %}
                    {{ "{:,}".format(lg.n_pixels) }}
                    {% if lg.cloud_pct is not none %}
                      <br/><span style="font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;">
                        ☁ {{ "%.0f"|format(lg.cloud_pct) }}%
                      </span>
                    {% endif %}
                  {% else %}
                    —
                  {% endif %}
                </td>
                <td style="padding:10px 12px;text-align:center;">
                  {% if lg.sem_observacao_recente %}
                    <span style="background-color:#94a3b8;color:#fff;
                                 padding:3px 10px;border-radius:3px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;">
                      SEM DADOS
                    </span>
                  {% else %}
                    <span style="background-color:{{ lg.status_color }};color:#fff;
                                 padding:3px 10px;border-radius:3px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;">
                      {{ lg.status | upper }}
                    </span>
                  {% endif %}
                </td>
              </tr>
              {% endfor %}
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Legenda de cores -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:0 32px 24px;">
            <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td style="font-size:12px;color:#64748b;padding-right:8px;">Legenda NDCI:</td>
                <td style="padding-right:6px;">
                  <span style="background-color:#22c55e;color:#fff;padding:2px 8px;
                               border-radius:3px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;">BOM</span>
                </td>
                <td style="font-size:11px;color:#64748b;padding-right:10px;">&lt; 0,02</td>
                <td style="padding-right:6px;">
                  <span style="background-color:#eab308;color:#fff;padding:2px 8px;
                               border-radius:3px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;">MODERADO</span>
                </td>
                <td style="font-size:11px;color:#64748b;padding-right:10px;">0,02–0,10</td>
                <td style="padding-right:6px;">
                  <span style="background-color:#f97316;color:#fff;padding:2px 8px;
                               border-radius:3px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;">ELEVADO</span>
                </td>
                <td style="font-size:11px;color:#64748b;padding-right:10px;">0,10–0,20</td>
                <td style="padding-right:6px;">
                  <span style="background-color:#ef4444;color:#fff;padding:2px 8px;
                               border-radius:3px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;">CRÍTICO</span>
                </td>
                <td style="font-size:11px;color:#64748b;">&gt; 0,20</td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Nota sobre cobertura de nuvens -->
        {% set sem_dados = lagoas | selectattr("sem_observacao_recente") | list %}
        {% if sem_dados %}
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:0 32px 20px;">
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
                   style="background-color:#f1f5f9;border-radius:4px;">
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:12px 16px;font-size:12px;color:#475569;">
                  <strong>Lagoas sem observação recente</strong>
                  (janela de {{ lookback_days }} dias):
                  {% for lg in sem_dados %}{{ lg.lagoa }}{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}.
                  Possíveis causas: cobertura de nuvens elevada ou passagem do satélite ainda
                  não processada. O próximo boletim incluirá os dados assim que disponíveis.
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endif %}

        <!-- Rodapé -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background-color:#f8fafc;border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;
                     padding:20px 32px;border-radius:0 0 8px 8px;">
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td style="font-size:12px;color:#64748b;">
                  <p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">
                    <a href="https://drklucas.github.io/lagoas/"
                       style="color:#1a4a7a;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
                      Acessar dashboard completo →
                    </a>
                  </p>
                  <p style="margin:0;color:#94a3b8;">
                    Satélite: Sentinel-2 (COPERNICUS/S2_SR_HARMONIZED) via Google Earth Engine.
                    Metodologia: Pi &amp; Guasselli, SBSR 2025.
                    Limiar de eflorescência ≈ 14 µg/L (NDCI ≈ 0,10).
                  </p>
                </td>
                <td align="right" valign="bottom" style="white-space:nowrap;">
                  <p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#cbd5e1;">
                    NDCI/Sentinel-2 · IFRS Osório
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

      </table><!-- fim container -->

    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
